Layout record Header has tag: u8; length: u16; flags: u8.

To parse header bytes: buffer of (size of Header) u8, giving i32.
Check length of bytes is equal to size of Header.
Let header be read Header from bytes at 0.
Give header.tag as i32.

To main, giving i32.
Let bytes be buffer of (size of Header) u8 filled with 0.
bytes at 0 becomes 7.
Give parse header bytes.
